title: Cassiopeia skin when?
body: Like really, yet another annie skin but no cass skin in more than three years? O.o dah cass hate is real

replies.body: No Yorick skin in 5 years. He only has his ones from release.
I would like to see either a "Heartseeker" Cassiopeia, a "Pentakill Fan" Cassiopeia or a "Dragon Tamer" Cassiopeia.
well you could have looked it up before flaming, but she is getting reworked and all champs in the process of getting reworked will not get a skin until  they are done getting reworked
